dcterms:description: A dataset containing records of users obtaining badges from the website Stack Overflow, which is a forum for programmers. The dataset includes 22 types of badges available, used as the mark of each event.
dcterms:title: StackOverflow (SO)

dcterms:description: A dataset recording the timestamps of retweets on Twitter within a certain period of time. The marks of the events denote the types of users who retweet, categorized into 'small', 'medium', and 'large' users based on their follower count.
dcterms:title: Retweet

dcterms:description: A music-related dataset containing records of songs listened to by certain users, with events marked by the singer of the song. This dataset includes over 3000 mark types.
dcterms:title: LastFM
